  "body": "<p>Hello fangerines! It’s <a href=\"http://abstractinspiration.com/\">Zinia</a> here and today I want to share with you a little minibook I created with the new Hustle &amp; Heart collection by Amy Tangerine!</p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/993b6ac8a43e5501.jpg?v=1782796776\"/>\n\n\n</figure>\n\n\n<p>The idea came to me when I first saw the square cut apart sheet that comes in this collection. I thought that these 3x3 squares would be perfect as pages for a minibook. I decided to work in an accordion mini cause it’s fun and cute.</p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<p>To create the base of the minibook I used two 12” long strips of paper and I cut them down to 3” wide. Then I folded my strips twice into an accordion shape and attached them together to make my minibook longer.</p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/96277a6038a4acfe.jpg?v=1782796779\"/>\n\n\n<figcaption>\n<p>I really wanted to keep the whole project very simple and time friendly so to simplify the process I used one photo and one 3x3 square from the cut apart sheet for every spread.</p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/53ffc8366ebd2bba.jpg?v=1782796781\"/>\n\n\n<figcaption>\n<p>To embellish my pages I used a combination of Hustle &amp; Heart as well as a few bits from Oh Happy Life collection.</p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/79b26503f66bf866.jpg?v=1782796784\"/>\n\n\n<figcaption>\n<p>Although I wanted to keep things flat and avoid extra bulk on my pages, I couldn’t resist using the gorgeous suede bows from Hustle &amp; Heart. They are my most favorite embellishment ever!</p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/51d0253ea17d4e04.jpg?v=1782796787\"/>\n\n\n<figcaption>\n<p>I also had a lot of fun with the clear stickers. Even though I usually prefer cardstock stickers, the sticker book from Hustle &amp; Heart is absolutely amazing! There are a ton of pages and you get a many gold and white stickers which can be stuck on top of dark patterns and surfaces.</p><p>Zinia<br/><br/><a href=\"http://abstractinspiration.com/\">Abstract Inspiration Blog</a> | <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/abstractinspiration/\">Instagram</a> | <a href=\"https://twitter.com/AbstractInsp\">Twitter</a> | <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/AbstractInspirationPage\">Facebook</a></p><p><strong>SUPPLY LIST:</strong></p><p>341869 Hustle &amp; Heart - 12x12 Paper Fit to Be Square | 341886 Hustle &amp; Heart - THICKERS Memento White | 341887 Hustle &amp; Heart - THICKERS The Lucky Ones | 341884 Hustle &amp; Heart - STICKER BOOK | 341889 Hustle &amp; Heart - PUFFY HEARTS | 341892 Hustle &amp; Heart - 3D DIAMOND STICKERS | 341893 Hustle &amp; Heart - MINI FAUX SUEDE BOWS | 376238 Oh Happy Life - PUFFY STICKERS | 376224 Oh Happy Life - EPHEMERA</p><p><em>Thanks so much for sharing this adorable minibook, Zinia! Other Design Team member posts can be found </em><a href=\"http://www.amytangerine.com/blog/?category=amy+tangerine+design+team\"><em>here</em></a><em>. Shop HUSTLE &amp; HEART now! Check your local retailer and online at </em><a href=\"http://bit.ly/AThustleandheart\"><em>Simon Says Stamp</em></a><em> and </em><a href=\"http://bit.ly/2vJOlKd\"><em>Scrapbook.com</em></a></p><p><em>Disclosure: Some of the links above are affiliate links. I receive a small percentage of sales at no cost to you. My creative partners and I really appreciate your continued support and every little bit helps me to bring you consistent content!</em></p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure>"
}